[
    {
        "text": "At Rolls-Royce, when conceiving new Ghost,...",
        "startTime": 1242,
        "endTime": 3884,
        "slowStartTime": 2013,
        "slowEndTime": 6051
    },
    {
        "text": "...our team kept returning to this phrase: Post Opulence.",
        "startTime": 4281,
        "endTime": 7992,
        "slowStartTime": 6571,
        "slowEndTime": 12213
    },
    {
        "text": "As a designer, when I imagine this movement I think of The Shard on London South Bank.",
        "startTime": 8509,
        "endTime": 13412,
        "slowStartTime": 12913,
        "slowEndTime": 20343
    },
    {
        "text": "It's the polar opposite of the opulent baroque buildings that it overlooks.",
        "startTime": 14076,
        "endTime": 18175,
        "slowStartTime": 21264,
        "slowEndTime": 27487
    },
    {
        "text": "It's perfectly minimal and linear,...",
        "startTime": 18865,
        "endTime": 21040,
        "slowStartTime": 28448,
        "slowEndTime": 31785
    },
    {
        "text": "...yet by cleverly using reflection and light, it doesn't feel clinical.",
        "startTime": 21573,
        "endTime": 25516,
        "slowStartTime": 32509,
        "slowEndTime": 38499
    },
    {
        "text": "It doesn't expend any excess energy to define itself.",
        "startTime": 26356,
        "endTime": 29495,
        "slowStartTime": 39684,
        "slowEndTime": 44467
    },
    {
        "text": "This is exactly what our Ghost clients asked us to create.",
        "startTime": 30464,
        "endTime": 33437,
        "slowStartTime": 45846,
        "slowEndTime": 50381
    },
    {
        "text": "They didn't want grandeur or fuss.",
        "startTime": 34097,
        "endTime": 35757,
        "slowStartTime": 51295,
        "slowEndTime": 53860
    },
    {
        "text": "They wanted something pure and clean.",
        "startTime": 36347,
        "endTime": 38061,
        "slowStartTime": 54670,
        "slowEndTime": 57317
    },
    {
        "text": "We removed all unnecessary design.",
        "startTime": 38737,
        "endTime": 41195,
        "slowStartTime": 58256,
        "slowEndTime": 62018
    },
    {
        "text": "We deleted shut lines.",
        "startTime": 41624,
        "endTime": 42883,
        "slowStartTime": 62586,
        "slowEndTime": 64549
    },
    {
        "text": "We pursued a minimal aesthetic...",
        "startTime": 43017,
        "endTime": 44793,
        "slowStartTime": 64675,
        "slowEndTime": 67415
    },
    {
        "text": "...whilst ensuring that the new Ghost was unmistakably a Rolls-Royce.",
        "startTime": 45199,
        "endTime": 49267,
        "slowStartTime": 67949,
        "slowEndTime": 74125
    },
    {
        "text": "And along the way,...",
        "startTime": 49933,
        "endTime": 50789,
        "slowStartTime": 75049,
        "slowEndTime": 76408
    },
    {
        "text": "...we discovered that creating perfect simplicity is really, really complex.",
        "startTime": 50943,
        "endTime": 56156,
        "slowStartTime": 76564,
        "slowEndTime": 84459
    },
    {
        "text": "To achieve it on new Ghost, we had to take huge steps,...",
        "startTime": 57159,
        "endTime": 60639,
        "slowStartTime": 85889,
        "slowEndTime": 91183
    },
    {
        "text": "...such as hand welding aluminium bodies...",
        "startTime": 61415,
        "endTime": 63509,
        "slowStartTime": 92272,
        "slowEndTime": 95488
    },
    {
        "text": "...and sewing incredibly long perfectly straight stitch lines.",
        "startTime": 63983,
        "endTime": 67649,
        "slowStartTime": 96125,
        "slowEndTime": 101698
    },
    {
        "text": "We had to find futuristic new materials.",
        "startTime": 68059,
        "endTime": 70857,
        "slowStartTime": 102239,
        "slowEndTime": 106511
    },
    {
        "text": "And to complement this,...",
        "startTime": 71517,
        "endTime": 72462,
        "slowStartTime": 107426,
        "slowEndTime": 108918
    },
    {
        "text": "...our engineers completely reconfigured our Rolls-Royce architecture.",
        "startTime": 72574,
        "endTime": 75867,
        "slowStartTime": 109011,
        "slowEndTime": 114026
    },
    {
        "text": "They distilled the experience of Ghost,...",
        "startTime": 76349,
        "endTime": 78187,
        "slowStartTime": 114673,
        "slowEndTime": 117506
    },
    {
        "text": "...imbuing it with an incredibly pure and refined driving personality.",
        "startTime": 78605,
        "endTime": 82499,
        "slowStartTime": 118057,
        "slowEndTime": 123973
    },
    {
        "text": "Because this particular group of our clients...",
        "startTime": 83678,
        "endTime": 85771,
        "slowStartTime": 125667,
        "slowEndTime": 128881
    },
    {
        "text": "..expressed a desire for something even more refined...",
        "startTime": 86175,
        "endTime": 88788,
        "slowStartTime": 129413,
        "slowEndTime": 133407
    },
    {
        "text": "...and even more pure than their existing Ghost.",
        "startTime": 89203,
        "endTime": 91753,
        "slowStartTime": 133954,
        "slowEndTime": 137854
    },
    {
        "text": "But still, in every respect, a true Rolls-Royce.",
        "startTime": 92665,
        "endTime": 96454,
        "slowStartTime": 139148,
        "slowEndTime": 144906
    }
]